title: Mass nickname changer (rewrite only)
description:
This cog lets you change/reset everyones nickname on a server at once.
The two commands that come with this cog are
- `massnick/mn [new nickname]` to enable/reset it and
- `resetnicks/rn` to remove all nicknames on the server.

[(Check the Source Code)](https://github.com/Bluscream/Discord-Selfbot-Cogs/blob/master/massnick.py)
